high_descs: Walk around the center table to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk around the center table to face the potato on the far side of the table.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Look up to face the pot on the center table.
Place the knife in the pot on the center table.
Walk around to face the potato on the opposite side of the center table.
Pick up a potato slice on the center table.
walk around the table to face the opposite side.
Place the potato slice in the pot on the center table.
Pick up the pot on the center table.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife and a potato slice a pot as well as move them to the sink.

high_descs: turn left, then go straight past the middle counter top to face the sink
pick up the knife in the sink
turn around, go straight, and then make a right to face the counter top behind the bar stools
slice the potato to the right of the tea kettle
go around to the opposite side of the center counter top
place the knife in the pot on the counter top
return to the other side of the counter top and face the sliced potato
pick up a slice of potato on the counter top
return to the other side of the center counter top facing the pot with the knife inside it
place the potato slice inside the pot on the counter top
pick up the pot on the counter top
go to the kitchen sink
place the pot on the left side of the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: slice a potato and place it in a pot for cooking preparation

high_descs: Turn left and go to the kitchen sink on the right.
Pick up the gray knife in the sink.
Turn around and go to the other side of the island that has potato on top.
Slice a half of the potato on the table.
Go around to the other side of the island that has a salt shaker.
Place the knife in the gray pot in the middle of the island.
Go around the island to the other side with the sliced potato.
Pick up one slice of the potato from the counter.
Go around the island back to the other side with the gray pot.
Place the potato slice into the pot next to the knife.
Pick up the pot with the knife and potato slice from the counter.
Turn right to go to the front of the sink on the right.
Place the pot with the knife and potato slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the knife and potato slice into the sink.
